name: Dr. House
body:
### Welcome to Dr. House!
We are Medical Clinical History App that will give you control and security over personal and family health and wellbeing.

![LoginSimulator](https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/skygear-cloud-asset/appsite/f0b883a1-d7eb-4a9b-aba7-935b05da2d3e-screenshot.png)

### Authors and Contributors
Please contact @akawer for any questions, suggestions or if you want to try the app out!

You can also check out my website at <http://akawer.github.io/>

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with the App? Check out our [documentation](https://drive.google.com/open?id=0BxY11mCa2mSQMVNSQnJRM3MzcFE) or [contact support](<aaronkawer@gmail.com>) and weâ€™ll help you sort it out.
